@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1 class="title">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<body class="privacy">

    <h1>Privacy Speech for Cash Register Webpage</h1>

    <p>Greetings valued customers and users of our Cash Register Webpage,</p>

    <p>I am honored to address you on behalf of our team and share important information regarding your privacy and data security.</p>

    <p>We are committed to ensuring the privacy and security of your personal information. As you interact with our Cash Register Webpage, we want you to feel confident that your data is handled responsibly and transparently.</p>

    <ol>
        <li>
            <strong>Data Collection:</strong>
            We collect only the necessary information required for the functionality of our cash register services. This includes transaction details, user preferences, and any additional information needed to provide a seamless experience.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Data Security:</strong>
            Your security is our top priority. We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. Our systems are regularly updated to ensure they meet the latest security standards.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Information Usage:</strong>
            The information you provide is used solely for the purpose of facilitating your transactions and improving our services. We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties without your consent.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Cookies and Analytics:</strong>
            Our website may use cookies and analytics tools to enhance your browsing experience. These tools help us understand how you use our services, allowing us to make improvements. You have the option to manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Compliance with Laws:</strong>
            We adhere to applicable privacy laws and regulations to safeguard your rights and ensure ethical data handling practices. If there are any changes to our privacy policy, we will promptly update you.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Your Control:</strong>
            We believe in empowering you. You have the right to access, modify, or delete your personal information. If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy, our support team is ready to assist you.
        </li>
    </ol>

    <p>In conclusion, your trust is of utmost importance to us. We are committed to maintaining the highest standards of privacy and data security. Thank you for choosing us. We appreciate your continued support as we work together to make your cash register experience safe, secure, and user-friendly.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions or feedback regarding our privacy practices, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

    <p>Thank you.</p>

    <p class="right">
        Victor Salinas<br>
        Programmer<br>
    </p>

</body>
